caption.text:
"SHARK FINNING"

Shark fin soup is a very luxurious dish in china, a bowl can be priced for $ 100. The demand of shark fin is very large. Every year, about 73 million shark fins are taken to be used as soup, or about 200,000 in a day. Averagely shark transported to a ship alive, fin cutted, then released back into the sea with bloody body. That shark will surely die sinking in the sea and loss of blood.
One of the largest suppliers of shark fin is Indonesia. Located in Karangsong fish auction market, Indramayu. Approximately 486 tons of dried shark fins are exported every year. Sadly shark finning in Indoneia is still difficult to control. An organization called WildAid said that from 14 shark species that commonly fin taken, almost entirely experiencing population decline of about 40-99%. .
.
.

"ANIMAL CRUELTY"

I am Ashariah S Wijaya, currently studying Film and Television at Universitas Multimedia Nusantara Indonesia.
Recently I upload 5 photos. These photos are an essay assignment for Visual Storytelling Class final test. My roles are photographer, props making, makeup artist and editor. 
Thank you so much for @zaqiaramallah , my lecture. Without her I can't finish these photos.
Thank you for my sisters, @amaliyahsofura and Nisa for being a model.
And thank you for @febryo14 for lending me the background for photo.
Plus thank you for all people that help me and gives me support that I can't tell one by one.

I choose animal cruelty as my main theme because I want to tell people the sad truth in this world. Many people still lack of information about animal cruelty. I hope with my photo, I can help increasing awareness with animal cruelty and decreasing animal cruelty in this world. .
.

caption.text:
"ABUSED IN TOURIST AREA"

In 8th of August 2016, netizens are busy talking about owl in a tourist area located in Sikidang Crater, Dieng Plateau. Start from a complaint from a woman named Raisa Ghifari, she said that the owls in that area used as an object of photograph during the day and forced to be awake, whereas the owl is a nocturnal animal. The owl owner spray the owl with water so it awake and able to used for photos. This is certainly pathetic, plus the weather is very hot in daytime.
Indeed, not all types of owls are nocturnal animal. Only around 60% of owls are nocturnal. This makes me to find out whether the owl in Dieng is nocturnal or not. From a source I get, one of the species of owl in Dieng is Bubo Sumatranus. And it's true, that species is a nocturnal with a characteristic of black eyes entirely.
.
.
.

"KILLED FOR FASHION?" An organization called PETA, did an investigation in 2015 about crocodiles and alligators exploitation in a crocodile farm named Lone Star Alligator Farm in Winie, Texas. This crocodile farm is a leather supplier for a large fashion industry, Hermes. From the investigation, fact obtained that crocodile be skinned alive and the skin is used for a Birkin Bags at a price $40.000 and a watch at a price $2.000.
Every year, around 43.000 crocodiles be killed. The situation in crocodile cage is very pathetic, a cage can be filled with 220 crocodiles. The crocodile skinned age is only 3 years old, while in the wild crocodiles can lived longer than human. Crocodile in the farm shot by a bolt gun on the head, then the throat will be cut and then skinned. Skin used is an abdomen skin, and for one Birkin Bag needs skin from 3 crocodiles.
.
.
.
#saveanimals #stopanimalabuse #stopanimalcruelty #animalabuse #animalcruelty #savewildlife #crocodile #alligator #hermes #birkinbag #kill #nikon #photography #conceptualphotography #photoshop

"FUR INDUSTRY"

Animal fur farms are growing a lot and very alarming. An animal protection organization, PETA Asia, conducting an investigations to China which is the largest exporter of animal fur such as raccoons, foxes, dogs, and rabbits.
One of them is rabbit. Rabbits are usually killed for their fur at the age of 6 months. The state of the cage is very poor, rabbit left in the outdoor cage with extreme weather. This extreme weather believed able to make the quality of rabbits fur increases. And no rabbits be vaccinated or getting treatment in this farm.
At the slaughterhouse, rabbits hit on the head using the handle of a knife then hung upside down. Without checking the rabbit is dead or not, they directly skinned the rabbit. Quite often when skinned, the rabbit still thrashing in pain. And sometimes the rabbit stunned using an electric gun.
.
.
.
#saveanimals #animalcruelty #animalabuse #stopanimalcruelty #stopanimalabuse #furindustry #fur #fashion #rabbit #photography #nikon #conceptualphotography

"RHINO POACHING"

Five rhino species are experiencing extinction. There are Black African Rhino with population less than 5.000, Indian Rhino and Nepal with population of 3.000, and Sumatran Rhino and Java with population less than 1.000.
Rhino horns have a function for defense and fight in the wild. But human hunt rhino horn to be sold because believe that the horn can be used for cure cancer and as a symbol of power for the rich. In black market, rhino horn can be priced for ¬£1,190 per ons. A statistic of rhino poaching in Africa shows that in 8 years, around 5.000 rhino be hunted.
Rhino sedated then the horn taken with a saw even machete. And usually there will be a very large wound with blood continually flow from its horn. It cause the rhino feel pain, and hard to breathe. The open wound can cause rhino died.
.
.
.

Terima kasih guru-guru lainnya yang tak bisa saya sebutkan satu per satu. 
Terima kasih seluruh panitia Dasanindya atas kerja keras kalian. 
Dan juga terima kasih untuk seluruh teman-teman yang selalu membantu dan mendukung saya.

Sebuah logo yang sangat berarti, sebuah logo dengan beragam filosofi. Terima kasih banyak Pak Tama atas bimbingannya~

Bagian utama logo membentuk huruf D yang terbentuk dari angka 1 dan 0, hal ini melambangkan Dasanindya, angkatan ke-10 SMK Bhakti Anindya. 
Bagian lengkung D atau angka 0 berbentuk irisan buah apel, melambangkan kota Batu - Malang. 
Di samping angka 1 terdapat ornamen yang berasal dari logo SMK Bhakti Anindya, melambangkan identitas darimana logo tersebut berasal.
